text: Melsheimer is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Ernst Melsheimer (1897–1960), German lawyer *Frederick Valentine Melsheimer (1749–1814), American entomologist and Lutheran clergyman *Frederick Ernst Melsheimer (1782–1873), American entomologist *Thomas M. Melsheimer, American lawyer and managing partner of Winston & Strawn LLP's Dallas office == See also == *Melsheimer FM-1, is an American single-seat, high-wing, FAI Open Class glider
